{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521890/extras/HoH-Features_2.png?t=1733339211\" /><br><strong>Hues of Hope</strong> is a colorful adventure where you play as a painter on a mission to recolor the world using elemental magic. Solve puzzles, explore Chromacia, and prepare for thrilling encounters with evil that can only be defeated by using colors and their corresponding elements to restore harmony.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521890/extras/Untitled_10.gif?t=1733339211\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521890/extras/HoH-Combat1.png?t=1733339211\" /><br><strong>Use your brush</strong> to dodge attacks, smash enemies and bring back joy into the world of Chromacia.<br><strong>Mix colors</strong> to optimize the damage against the uprising evil and fight the decolorization with the help of your elemental magic.<br><strong>Combine the power</strong> of <i>water</i>, <i>fire</i>, <i>nature</i>, <i>wind</i> and <i>love</i> in different ways to banish the evil forces that came to destroy peace and harmony.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521890/extras/HoH-Story1.png?t=1733339211\" /><br>In a world where color and happiness got banished you get one last chance to fight the evil. Take your brush and palette, reclaim the elemental magic and recolor the world of chromacia.<br><br><br><br><i>More coming soon...</i>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521890/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733339211","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521890/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1733339211","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521890/capsule_231x87.jpg?t